snippet.title: [Kaze's F3 2018] Bounce Tales 64 Trailer [Old]
snippet.description:
Trailer of my upcoming hack called Bounce Tales 64 for F3.

EDIT: This trailer is now outdated, i fixed most of the textures and now level 4 has water like in the original game. The quicksand and lava thing were just for test. Also I'm aiming to make it console compatible.

Hack64 post (will update it later): https://hack64.net/Thread-Bounce-Tales-64
